{"tid":1390213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求政府清算元朗白衣人 要求入暴動罪","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:40:10.000Z","uid":224453,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97f2ba705b29fc1e560701a57563bc935e76fc3f","tid":1390213,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:49:51.000Z","msg":"及警察人為失當<br />\n<br />\n點解我哋班義士冇做過啲咩 要俾人入暴動罪 <br />\n<br />\n望吓元朗班仆街 手持鐵通藤條 警察睇唔到？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老豆本身係中立 自從見到元朗單野發生之後 <br />\n<br />\n不斷係咁屌政府同中聯辦  班後生本身前途好好 <br />\n<br />\n為咗香港好 而斷送自己前途 政府你瞓醒未<br />\n<br />\n依家香港冇咗中立 全部則埋一邊 <br />\n<br />\n上環嗰邊已經全部提堂檢控 <br />\n<br />\n元朗嗰邊呢 係咪要拖兩三年 好似朱Sir咁？？？<br />\n<br />\n我個心真係好痛 點解政府要咁對啲年青人<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位巴絲打 加油 幫我行埋落去"},{"pid":"9f1b7216160654d78210722cc58cb1f061a16b5f","tid":1390213,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f6fee27e612f42b5ef23c152b0da2f5851fefb6f","tid":1390213,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"白衫都係中共既人<br />\n黑警又係中共既人<br />\n佢地做乜都無人制裁到"},{"pid":"0c2b0f8d65c4be8587f82c4350671df579d9fad5","tid":1390213,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c865f49dd206ee988b10262587cbbc99eaab1fd9","tid":1390213,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:32:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd72e97751b9bf4064c7856b5d44a0b884948e8a","tid":1390213,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:32:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e7b47058ad37779fcea2698df75477297337c2e2","